Month ago ตรวจ routine surveillance: serum AST 88, ALT 76, ALP 320, GGT 240; CT chest: 2 lung nodules 8-10 mm; CT abdomen: 3 liver lesions 1-2 cm enhancing; tumor markers CEA, CA 15-3 elevated

